15. Sed video. [Here Syrus at length pereeives Clitipho and Clinia] - 0 Jupiter. Nothing can be more moving or expressive than this complerint, wherein we see the lover brought to the very brink of despair; for it was necessary to carry the mistake as far as possible, before he should be undeceived. We are to suppose his words too accompanied with gestures equally expressive of his grief, till Syrus, approaching nearer, perceiving the error, clears Antiphila of those unjust suspicions, by the long and elegant account of her which follows. -- Ubinam est fides?
